               <CRITERIA_CANDIDATE>
                  <P>An open Day was held at Bath &amp; North East Somerset Council on 22nd March for interested companies. It was attended by 27 organisations. Although under this procedure we are able to limit the number of companies to 3, we have decided that in this instance, due to the number of companies of that have expressed an interest, we should increase this to 5.</P>
               </CRITERIA_CANDIDATE>
               <NO_ACCEPTED_VARIANTS/>
               <OPTIONS/>
               <OPTIONS_DESCR>
                  <P>The contract will be for a 7 year term (84 months) with options to extend for a further period of up to 10 years (120 months) subject to satisfactory performance and re-appraisal of financial accounts and other due diligence requirements. The extension will be up to an additional 3 years and will be subject to performance and due diligence checks.</P>
               </OPTIONS_DESCR>
